        <header class="text-center mb-12">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-800">Interventional Radiology Fundamentals</h1>
            <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">An interactive guide to the essential tools of IR: needles, guidewires, catheters, and sheaths.</p>
